.TH AI-PLAYBOOK-EDIT 1 "" "ai-playbook" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ai\-playbook\-edit \- Open a saved playbook in $EDITOR
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBai\-playbook\fR edit <slug>
.SH DESCRIPTION
edit resolves <slug> to its store file and opens it in $EDITOR.
.SH OPTIONS
This command takes no flags.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
ai\-playbook edit deploy\-staging
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBai\-playbook\fR(1)
